# React Rules

Always use:

- Functional components
- Hooks
- Named exports when appropriate

Component rules:

One responsibility per component.

Keep components under roughly 150 lines whenever possible.

Split UI into reusable pieces.

## State

Keep state local whenever possible.

Avoid prop drilling.

## Naming

Use:

PascalCase

Example:

Hero.jsx

MembershipCard.jsx

Navbar.jsx

Footer.jsx

CamelCase for:

Variables

Functions

Hooks

## File Structure

One component per file.

Avoid giant files.